{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"981dec072c","title":"草木篇","origin":"原载1957年1月成都出版的诗歌刊物《星星》创刊号，引自《鸣放言论(一)》（北京：“学习生活”编辑室编，1957年7月2日）；《四川省右派言论选辑9》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年8月26日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bfbfb23a99","index":0,"year":1956,"month":10,"day":30,"articleId":"981dec072c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"39ce2a4a60","name":"流沙河"},{"id":"a185c9b36c","name":"四川"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b864ca9dd9","type":"title","text":"草木篇","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"4aed4c53c8","type":"authors","text":"四川流沙河","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"f0a337b394","type":"subtitle","text":"（流沙河：四川成都诗人）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"423255d166","type":"paragraph","text":"寄言立身者  勿学柔弱苗——唐：白居易","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"d7595015d2","type":"subtitle","text":"白杨","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"38ed286ea1","type":"paragraph","text":"她，一柄绿光闪闪的长剑，孤零零地立在平原，高指蓝天。也许，一场暴风会把她连根拔去。但，纵然死了吧，她的腰也不肯向谁弯一弯！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"7cdf855204","type":"subtitle","text":"藤","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"be517ef2b5","type":"paragraph","text":"他纠缠着丁香，往上爬，爬，爬……终于把花挂上树梢。丁香被缠死了，砍作柴烧了。他倒在地上，喘着气，窥视着另一株树……","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"88f67c7305","type":"subtitle","text":"仙人掌","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"763c72329c","type":"paragraph","text":"她不想用鲜花向主人献媚，遍身披上刺刀。主人把她逐出花园，也不给水喝。在野地里，在沙漠中她活着，繁殖着儿女……","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"7c4caf3dcc","type":"subtitle","text":"梅","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"ebb2587436","type":"paragraph","text":"在姐姐妹妹里，她的爱情来得最迟。春天，百花用媚笑引诱蝴蝶的时候，她却把自己悄悄地许给了冬天的白雪。轻佻的蝴蝶是不配吻她的，正如别的花不配被白雪抚爱一样。在姐姐妹妹里，她笑得最晚，笑得最美丽。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"74d9ef32f2","type":"subtitle","text":"毒菌","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"97b3884d02","type":"paragraph","text":"在阳光照不到的河岸，他出现了。白天，用美丽的彩衣，黑夜，用暗绿的磷火，诱惑人类。然而，连三岁孩子也不去采他。因为，妈妈说过，那是毒蛇吐的唾液……","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"},{"id":"bf90d9833e","type":"paragraph","text":" 1956年10月30日","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c"}],"page":{"id":"0539891784","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"981dec072c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}